name: Wedding Night: I Am Forced To Marry A Dragon Girl
summary:
Jiang Xiaobai reincarnated to another world and was forced to marry a dragon. Moreover, it was a hot-tempered female dragon.



Jiang Xiaobai was in despair when he thought of his future of being tortured by his wife.



He could not choose his fate of being reincarnated, but he could choose to be a faithful man even though he had to marry an irascible dragon maiden!



[Ding! God-tier Option System has been activated after sensing your earnest summon.]



[Option 1: Marry her. Reward: Dragon Essence and Tiger Bone Pills]



[Option 2: Reject her. Reward: Demigod level cultivation]



[Option 3: Boldly speak your mind about her. Reward: Innate Body of the Way and God-level martial arts technique.]



Jiang Xiaobai wondered, “Should I marry her or should I reject her?”
author: Heaven Forbidden Killingtransmigration
